content:
Einstein Data Detect Is Now Data Detect

Einstein Data Detect is now called Data Detect. Product documentation and in-app wording are updated to reflect the new name. This change doesn't affect how Data Detect works or behaves.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

Who: The Data Detect managed package is available to customers who purchase the Salesforce Shield add-on subscription.

Salesforce Help: Data Detect
